# LEGACY BLOCKCHAIN (HTML dashboard)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------

### Get Legacy Chain
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/chain

###

### Get Legacy Balances
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/balances

